title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

“Audi's at reduced savings.” [An ad in The Hartford Courant, 6 July 1988. Submitted by Sidney Perlman, Hartford.]

Solution to Verbal Analogies II

1: Amalthea
2: Meconic
3: Pone
4: Hang Seng
5: A (u) stringer, Ostringer
6: Brevier
7: Ptolemy
8: Ichor
9: Excelsior
10: Edgar
11: Berceuse
12: Fustanella
